Executive Profile
Warren Jay Potter  Chief Financial Officer and Senior Vice President, Shiloh Industries, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 0 Board Members in 0 different organizations across 2 different industries.55$648,831As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. Warren Jay Potter, also known as Jay, has been the Chief Financial Officer and Senior Vice President of Shiloh Industries, Inc. since December 16, 2015. Mr. Potter has nearly 30 years of experience in finance and accounting, operations management, risk management and business development and expansion. He has held several senior financial leadership roles in a cross-section of industries including automotive, aerospace, building products and technology enabled services. ... During his career, he has played a key role in business expansion and M&A. He served as the Chief Financial Officer and Treasurer at Sedgwick Claims Management Services, Inc., from September 10, 2012 to August 24, 2015. He served as the Chief Financial Officer of Masco Cabinetry, a division of the Masco Corporation. He has also served in financial leadership roles for premier corporations including EFW Inc., St. Jude Medical and AlliedSignal. He is a Certified Public Accountant and earned the Six Sigma Green Belt designation. Mr. Potter holds both a Bachelor of Science degree in accounting and a Master of Business Administration degree from Indiana University.Read Full Background




