Insider Activity


Individual




Warren Jay Potter



Mr. Warren J. Potter is Chief Financial Officer & Senior Vice President at Shiloh Industries, Inc. and Chief Financial Officer at Merillat Industries LLC. 
Mr. Potter was previously employed as Treasurer by Sedgwick Claims Management Services, Inc., Director-Finance & Pricing by Alliedsignal Aerospace, Chief Financial Officer & Vice President Finance by EFW, Inc., Chief Financial Officer by Masco Cabinetry LLC, and Director-Finance & Cost Management by St. Jude Medical, Inc. 
He received his undergraduate degree from Indiana University and an MBA from Indiana University.



